Package: brfinance
Title: Simplified Access to Brazilian Financial Data
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "JoÃ£o Paulo", 
           family = "dos Santos Pereira Barbosa", 
           email = "joao.31582129@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides programmatic access to Brazilian economic and financial data, including interest rates (e.g., the SELIC base rate), unemployment figures, and other indicators from official sources such as the Central Bank of Brazil and IBGE. Data is returned in tidy format, ready for analysis.
